Package com.amazonaws.services.kinesis.samples.stocktrades

Example on getting data from Amazon Kinesis Streams into Splunk.

See: Description

Package com.amazonaws.services.kinesis.samples.stocktrades Description

Example on getting data from Amazon Kinesis Streams into Splunk. This package contains code to put dummy stock trade data into a Kinesis Stream (StockTradesWriter) and pull data from the stream and send it to Splunk (StockTradesProcessor).
